1. Whaat happens when you turn on your computer
	1. loads operating system into RAM
	2. programs are a set of instructions executed by the microprocessor
	3. instruction tells the microproessor what action to perform
		Arithmetic logic operation
		Read data from input device
		Write to memory
		Reset
		Stop
	4. Opcodes in assembly
		Like ADD A, B, C
		
		Opcodes are 7 bit instruction for the microprocessor
